{"tid":1150612,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南亞幫「收陀地」不遂淋油報復　公園阿叔變紅人","createTime":"2019-05-12T03:45:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-12T08:15:13.000Z","uid":51620,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"ae7718fc81d5bc78b4bfed2aeb3ee4a624c24860","tid":1150612,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T03:45:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190512/photo/bkn-20190512010748481-0512_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190512101017\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190512%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190512010748481-0512_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190512101017&h=ae0740b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n馬鞍山發生襲擊傷人案，昨晚(11日)10時許，多名長者在頌安邨頌德樓對開休憩公園閒聊，現場消息稱，其時附近亦有一批年約60至70歲老翁在聚賭，期間有2名戴口罩南亞裔男子趨前，向在場一名姓蕭(59歲)男子表示要「收陀地」，其時，當中有人答口：「收咩陀地？報警㗎！」南亞大漢聞言，其中一人取出一樽紅色漆油向在場人士淋潑，多人走避不及被淋中，部分人返回住所自行清理，並有2名遭淋中事主留在現場助查，包括一名赤膊，穿牛仔褲及拖鞋男子，以及一名穿T恤、西褲及涼鞋男子，其中赤膊男的臉、頸及雙手俱沾有油漬有如「紅人」。<br />\n<br />\n警員接報到場兜截惜無發現，案件列襲擊及有人受傷處理，並向在場人士了解案發經過，又根據事主描述追緝兇徒下落。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190512/bkn-20190512010748481-0512_00822_001.html?fbclid=IwAR0QzZbTz0YvFdrVST_RS8qbnnI74mMi6VdcFF51tZB4YBqmEjjsf05Ll48\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190512%2Fbkn-20190512010748481-0512_00822_001.html%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0QzZbTz0YvFdrVST_RS8qbnnI74mMi6VdcFF51tZB4YBqmEjjsf05Ll48&d=0a%2BBnfQRLGMOm4peNIjNW9LD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=6b2034d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190512/bkn-20190512010748481-0512_00822_001.html?fbclid=IwAR0QzZbTz0YvFdrVST_RS8qbnnI74mMi6VdcFF51tZB4YBqmEjjsf05Ll48</a>"},{"pid":"9ce73aaf3bcf81671f8f366d80472fe3fbcfff67","tid":1150612,"uid":160028,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T03:47:33.000Z","msg":"公園都收陀地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p